---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Refund Policy — Rumeira"
  description="Rumeira's refund policy for retainer-based digital marketing, website design, hosting, and software development services."
  canonical="https://rumeira.com/refund-policy"
>
  <Nav />
  <main id="main" class="pt-32 md:pt-40">
    <section class="container-x pb-24 md:pb-32">
      <header class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl leading-[1.05] md:text-6xl">Refund Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-base md:text-lg">
          <strong>Effective Date:</strong> January 1, 2023
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg">
          At <strong>Rumeira</strong> (&ldquo;Company&rdquo;), we provide professional digital marketing, website design,
          website hosting, and software development services. By engaging our services and submitting
          payment, you acknowledge and agree to the terms of this Refund Policy.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="legal-prose  max-w-3xl space-y-3 mt-6 text-base leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="!mt-5 text-2xl md:text-3xl">Retainer-Based Services</h2>
        <p>
          All services provided by Rumeira operate on a <strong>retainer basis</strong>. This ensures
          dedicated resources, priority scheduling, and continuous strategy implementation for your
          projects.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>
            <strong>Payment Requirement:</strong> Retainers must be paid in full prior to the commencement
            of any work or the continuation of monthly service cycles.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Nature of Work:</strong> Because our services involve immediate allocation of labor,
            intellectual property, and proprietary strategy, all payments are considered &ldquo;earned&rdquo;
            upon receipt.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="!mt-5 text-2xl md:text-3xl">No Refunds</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>All Sales are Final.</strong> Unless explicitly stated otherwise in a separate, signed
          Service Agreement:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>
            <strong>Service Delivery:</strong> We do not offer refunds for any payments made. This includes
            initial setup fees, monthly retainer payments, and deposits.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Electronic Consumption:</strong> Due to the nature of digital services&mdash;where
            insights, optimizations, and code are delivered and consumed in real-time&mdash;we cannot
            &ldquo;reclaim&rdquo; the value provided once work has started.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="!mt-5 text-2xl md:text-3xl">Cancellation of Services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>
            <strong>Notice Period:</strong> You may cancel your services at any time. To avoid future
            charges, notice must be provided via email to
            <a href="mailto:support@rumeira.com">support@rumeira.com</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>No Prorated Credits:</strong> Upon cancellation, any payment already processed for the
            current billing cycle is non-refundable. We do not provide credits or prorated refunds for
            unused days within a billing month.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Future Charges:</strong> Once a cancellation is confirmed, no further charges will be
            applied to your account for subsequent billing periods.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="!mt-5 text-2xl md:text-3xl">No Guarantees</h2>
        <p>
          While we strive for excellence, Rumeira does not guarantee specific performance outcomes, such as
          exact search engine rankings or specific traffic volumes. Digital performance is subject to
          third-party algorithms and market variables beyond our control.
        </p>

        <h2 class="!mt-5 text-2xl md:text-3xl">Disputes &amp; Chargebacks</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>
            <strong>Payment Processing:</strong> We utilize secure processors (such as Stripe) to manage
            transactions.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Dispute Resolution:</strong> In the event of a chargeback or payment dispute, Rumeira
            reserves the right to submit comprehensive evidence of services rendered, including project
            logs, communication records, and deliverables, to the financial institution.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="!mt-5 text-2xl md:text-3xl">Policy Changes</h2>
        <p>
          Rumeira reserves the right to modify this policy at any time. Updated versions will be posted on
          our website with a new Effective Date. Continued use of our services following an update
          constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="!mt-5 text-2xl md:text-3xl">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions regarding your retainer or this policy, please reach out to our support team:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong>
          <a href="mailto:support@rumeira.com">support@rumeira.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-prose h2 {
    color: #0a0a0a;
    font-family: "Satoshi", system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .legal-prose a {
    color: #987622;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .legal-prose a:hover {
    color: #bc922c;
  }
</style>
